raw_meta_yaml:
context:
  version: "0.3.9"

package:
  name: fastbencode
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/f/fastbencode/fastbencode-${{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: ded887be2e7eb4bc4dc27742ff5ef2242e13dc169348dc2c91cc5055aa2f8285

build:
  number: 0
  script:
    - cargo-bundle-licenses --format yaml --output THIRDPARTY.yml
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation

requirements:
  build:
    - ${{ compiler('c') }}
    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}
    - ${{ compiler('rust') }}
    - cargo-bundle-licenses
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - python
  host:
    - cython
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools
    - setuptools-rust
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports:
        - fastbencode
  - requirements:
      run:
        - pip
        - python
    script:
      - pip check

about:
  license: GPL-2.0-or-later
  license_file:
    - COPYING
    - THIRDPARTY.yml
  summary: Implementation of bencode with optional fast C extensions
  homepage: https://github.com/breezy-team/fastbencode

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - danielnachun
